{"tid":130340,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"Pccw轉plan JJ插欣宜求router","createTime":"2017-02-22T10:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T17:28:27.000Z","uid":82050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab2017c938695ebebbeb58ce2c351361e044259","tid":130340,"uid":82050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜轉(續)左個上網plan, 唔要pccw個wifi (好撚廢又好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />$68/月）<br />\n依家就得番個router,冇wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連之前192.168果個位都入唔到（定唔知係轉左定點）<br />\n上網睇過好似好多都唔太啱，因為個router係依個做輸入...<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9yjfb7nw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9yjfb7nw&h=a7e840eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知乜撚野頭黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/c3ilykba\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fc3ilykba&h=b23b97d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一面就接緊依件野<br />\n有咩router用到依個頭，定係要焗9住用佢個router之後再買過隻wifi用lan線駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"161df423a089b3ffd4522d162b2141cc7476e7da","tid":130340,"uid":27000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"綠色Optic fibre 頭黎<br />\n<br />\n你搵條lan求其插個port 未得囉"},{"pid":"522f6b2757139eda56aec2470a096a6859eeca58","tid":130340,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:32:12.000Z","msg":"個wifi唔係$18個月咩"},{"pid":"7b7477e48e951a9885620056dbf00ed93ef6f7ba","tid":130340,"uid":82050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個wifi唔係$18個月咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pccw 個新plan係咁撚貴我都冇計（所以我先唔續個wifi)"},{"pid":"11cfd468f741e4e88fc4a9c84efeb92aef889a20","tid":130340,"uid":45040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"咩plan先？<br />\nrouter 幾錢budget<br />\n牌子有冇要求，屋幾大"},{"pid":"2805a112a21326bb9584720a46044fe11705fd7b","tid":130340,"uid":82050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>綠色Optic fibre 頭黎<br />\n<br />\n你搵條lan求其插個port 未得囉</blockquote><br />\n就係唔想用佢個router, 買過一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢隻router一開始講就講全新啫，之前用左幾耐都唔知"},{"pid":"afccc245ec30c5d8f49a8c99c4d3fc402452f079","tid":130340,"uid":82050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩plan先？<br />\nrouter 幾錢budget<br />\n牌子有冇要求，屋幾大</blockquote><br />\n500mb<br />\n筆直太約 $400 <br />\n牌子方面冇咩要求 ， 屋就特殊少少（比埋隔離屋用），愈大就愈好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df21bc3843031637c215809e8b21d3ac6b7bfe6b","tid":130340,"uid":45040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"個個係光纖機，有得換，但換左你覺得pccw會話你知部野password咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfd98cadf70c69145034847c598776d8c525b87","tid":130340,"uid":82050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個係光纖機，有得換，但換左你覺得pccw會話你知部野password咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你話要換黑色定白色果部先"},{"pid":"d27683680a030916402b27a3a8e2e6106236df33","tid":130340,"uid":45040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩plan先？<br />\nrouter 幾錢budget<br />\n牌子有冇要求，屋幾大